<html>
  <head>
  </head>
  <body style='width: 100%;'>
    <header
      style='
        padding: 1rem;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #96bf01ff;
        width: 100%;
      '
    >
      <h2 style='font-size: 2rem; font-weight:700;'>Ruby Resorts</h2>
    </header>
    <section style='height:80vh; width:full; font-size:1.2rem'>
      <p>Warm greetings,
        <span
          style='font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight:700; color:#96bf01ff'
        >{{name}}</span></p>
      <p>
        We are thrilled to confirm your booking at [Resort Name]! Thank you for
        choosing us as your destination for relaxation and adventure. You can
        find your reservation details
      </p>
      <a
        target='_blank'
        style='background-color:#96bf01ff ; color:white; padding: 6px 4px; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block '
        href={{link}}
        role='button'
      >Your Reservation</a>
      <p>
        At Ruby Resorts, we strive to create memorable experiences for all our
        guests. Whether you plan to unwind by our pristine beaches, indulge in
        our gourmet dining options, or explore the local attractions, we are
        here to ensure your stay is perfect. If you have any special requests or
        need assistance with anything before your arrival, please don't hesitate
        to contact us.

      </p>
      <p>
        We look forward to welcoming you and making your stay unforgettable.
        Thank you once again for choosing Ruby Resorts. Safe travels, and see
        you soon!
      </p>
    </section>
    <footer style='border-top: 2px #96bf01ff solid;'>
      <h2 style='font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight:700; margin: 2rem 0rem'>Ruby
        Resorts Team</h2>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>